Examination Room

00:00:03.750 --> 00:00:05.870
Trainer, you're overreacting!

00:00:05.870 --> 00:00:08.320
I feel totally fine.

00:00:08.320 --> 00:00:09.800
Better safe than sorry.

00:00:09.800 --> 00:00:11.340
It doesn't hurt to have him take a look.

00:00:11.340 --> 00:00:15.690
I hope this doesn't take long! I wanna 
start my training for the Kikkashou.

00:00:15.690 --> 00:00:17.090
Tokai Teio-san?

00:00:17.090 --> 00:00:17.810
What's up?

00:00:17.810 --> 00:00:18.940
Your leg is broken.

00:00:19.870 --> 00:00:21.100
It's a fracture.

00:00:21.100 --> 00:00:23.600
You won't be racing again 
until spring of next year.

00:00:26.190 --> 00:00:27.500
I want you to check into the hospital.

00:00:26.190 --> 00:00:30.340
Please be quiet
in the hospital

00:00:27.500 --> 00:00:28.890
Th-The hospital?!

00:00:28.890 --> 00:00:35.720
No way! No way, no way, no way, no way!

00:00:30.340 --> 00:00:31.970
You're sure it's broken?

00:00:31.970 --> 00:00:33.250
It is.

00:00:33.250 --> 00:00:35.320
For now, I'm going to give 
her something for the pain.

