00:02:09.230 --> 00:02:10.540
What did you just say?

00:02:10.540 --> 00:02:12.920
I said, I'm running in the Kikkashou!

00:02:12.920 --> 00:02:14.510
Running? But you're...

00:02:12.920 --> 00:02:21.930
Fire
Extinguisher

00:02:13.480 --> 00:02:18.440
