00:13:16.120 --> 00:13:17.780
It's gotta have milk!

00:13:17.780 --> 00:13:19.210
You need that calcium.

00:13:19.210 --> 00:13:20.630
Oranges! For Vitamin C!

00:13:20.630 --> 00:13:22.230
Honey is a necessity as well!

00:13:22.230 --> 00:13:25.020
Carrots! It needs carrots! Even if it 
has nothing else, it needs carrots!

00:13:25.020 --> 00:13:26.170
Sounds good to me!

00:13:26.170 --> 00:13:28.830
And then we'll throw in some 
garlic for stamina boosting.

00:13:28.830 --> 00:13:29.590
Teio!

00:13:30.240 --> 00:13:31.670
What're you doing?

00:13:31.670 --> 00:13:35.810
We were coming up with 
a special drink for you!

00:13:35.810 --> 00:13:39.330
Honestly, and with my 
Tennoushou race coming up.

00:13:39.330 --> 00:13:40.680
Do some taste-testing for us.

00:13:40.680 --> 00:13:41.910
No garlic, though.

00:13:41.910 --> 00:13:43.110
Why the hell not?

00:13:43.670 --> 00:13:46.530
You guys are gonna listen 
to my opinion, right?

00:13:46.530 --> 00:13:48.230
So, can I put the garlic in?

00:13:48.230 --> 00:13:50.250
Obviously not!

