00:15:03.610 --> 00:15:05.610
Kikkashou Registration Form

00:15:03.610 --> 00:15:05.610
Spica

00:15:03.610 --> 00:15:05.610
Tokai Teio

00:15:07.260 --> 00:15:08.610
What else do we do?

00:15:08.610 --> 00:15:09.950
Change her shoes?

00:15:09.950 --> 00:15:13.490
But having her run in shoes 
she's not used to isn't realistic.

00:15:15.340 --> 00:15:18.230
There's a hot springs for 
horse girls in Iwaki.

00:15:18.230 --> 00:15:21.500
But doing something like that, 
so suddenly, carries a lot of risk.

00:15:21.500 --> 00:15:25.500
There are tights that work like 
support tape, but this is the G-1.

00:15:25.500 --> 00:15:28.130
There's just not enough time to incorporate 
it into her ensemble.

00:15:28.130 --> 00:15:31.380
Look at the mess you've made!

00:15:32.340 --> 00:15:34.570
Teio? How'd it go at the hospital?

00:15:35.230 --> 00:15:37.820
I've gotta keep my promise, huh?

00:15:41.970 --> 00:15:43.430
We hang in there until the last minute.

00:15:44.020 --> 00:15:48.820
But if the doctor says it's a no-go, 
then I have to give up. Right?

00:15:49.970 --> 00:15:51.750
As far as the Kikkashou goes—

00:15:51.750 --> 00:15:52.370
Not yet!

00:15:53.310 --> 00:15:57.660
We can't give up yet! 
There's gotta be something we can do.

00:15:57.660 --> 00:16:01.640
Teio, I swear, I'll help you become an 
undefeated Triple Crown winner!

00:16:01.640 --> 00:16:02.630
It's okay.

00:16:03.740 --> 00:16:04.640
I mean it.

00:16:05.460 --> 00:16:06.520
Teio...

00:16:07.090 --> 00:16:09.380
I still can't run at full strength.

00:16:09.380 --> 00:16:11.660
So the idea of entering the Kikkashou,

00:16:11.660 --> 00:16:13.870
and going up against everyone 
in their best condition...

00:16:14.550 --> 00:16:15.900
I just couldn't do that.

00:16:18.310 --> 00:16:20.770
Thank you for everything, though.

00:16:23.790 --> 00:16:26.150
Come on, don't give me that look!

00:16:26.150 --> 00:16:27.160
I'm sorry.

00:16:27.160 --> 00:16:28.880
Seriously, it's fine.

00:16:31.420 --> 00:16:32.870
Hey, Trainer...

00:16:32.870 --> 00:16:34.030
What's up?

00:16:34.030 --> 00:16:39.030
Kikkashou Registration Form

00:16:34.030 --> 00:16:39.030
Spica

00:16:34.030 --> 00:16:39.030
Tokai Teio

00:16:35.040 --> 00:16:36.770
Can you do me a favor?

00:16:37.160 --> 00:16:41.040
Kikkashou

00:16:37.160 --> 00:16:41.040
Kyoto Racecourse

00:16:49.120 --> 00:16:51.100
Thanks for bringing me.

00:16:51.580 --> 00:16:52.380
Sure.

00:16:59.150 --> 00:17:02.510
You want something to eat, Teio? My treat.

00:17:02.510 --> 00:17:06.030
Then I'll have some grilled carrots, 
carrot juice, and a chocolate covered banana.

00:17:06.030 --> 00:17:08.270
Wow, could you show some restraint?

00:17:08.570 --> 00:17:09.410
Please.

00:17:11.160 --> 00:17:12.030
I'll just be a sec.

00:17:19.420 --> 00:17:21.730
You're not going to talk to her?

00:17:21.730 --> 00:17:23.140
There's no need.

00:17:23.140 --> 00:17:26.200
I know Teio isn't the kind of horse girl 
to let something like this stop her.

00:17:26.620 --> 00:17:30.670
Are you sure it's not that 
you can't find the words?

00:17:30.670 --> 00:17:31.930
That's harsh of you...

00:17:31.930 --> 00:17:33.160
Sorry.

00:17:34.420 --> 00:17:35.620
But you're right.

00:17:37.490 --> 00:17:38.230
Please...

00:17:39.210 --> 00:17:41.530
Keep fighting your way forward, Teio.

00:17:42.330 --> 00:17:44.020
It's a beautiful day here 
at the Kyoto Racecourse,

00:17:44.020 --> 00:17:47.890
but which horse girl will be going 
home with the the chrysanthemum medal?

00:17:48.160 --> 00:17:50.200
It's a shame how things 
turned out for Tokai Teio.

00:17:50.200 --> 00:17:52.480
It would've been quite a sight, 
seeing her take the Triple Crown.

00:17:52.710 --> 00:17:55.390
A lot of attention is focused on Rionatal, 
who came in second place at the Derby,

00:17:55.390 --> 00:17:57.950
and Nice Nature, who is 
currently on a four-win streak.

00:17:57.950 --> 00:17:58.980
I have to agree.

00:17:58.980 --> 00:18:02.780
They both look very calm. 
I think we can expect big things.

00:18:22.600 --> 00:18:25.060
All horse girls are now at the gate.

00:18:25.350 --> 00:18:26.630
And the Kikkashou...

00:18:28.850 --> 00:18:30.060
Kyoto

00:18:30.060 --> 00:18:31.450
...is off to a beautiful start!

00:18:31.450 --> 00:18:34.460
They've all taken off, as the 
pack slowly starts to extend.

00:18:34.460 --> 00:18:37.570
In the lead is Nanto Mist, 
followed by Shinano Orange,

00:18:37.570 --> 00:18:40.750
with K2 Suisan coming up on the inside, 
and Rionatal moving up from the outside.

00:18:38.990 --> 00:18:40.750
It's started.

00:18:40.750 --> 00:18:42.850
The race has started out 
a slightly faster pace.

00:18:42.850 --> 00:18:44.580
Nice Nature in the back.

00:18:44.580 --> 00:18:47.080
She's on a four-win streak, so I think we'll 
see something special today.

00:18:47.080 --> 00:18:50.230
The crowd's cheers are washing 
over these horse girls.

00:18:50.230 --> 00:18:52.090
You have to wonder if being 
able to keep their cool

00:18:52.090 --> 00:18:54.700
will be the determining factor 
in who comes out ahead.

00:18:55.150 --> 00:18:58.550
If it was me, I'd head to the middle.

00:18:59.220 --> 00:19:00.840
Then I'd check things out.

00:19:01.550 --> 00:19:04.440
The girl I raced against in the 
Derby would be next to me.

00:19:05.230 --> 00:19:08.730
And Nature would be behind me, 
but I know she'd be coming for me.

00:19:09.730 --> 00:19:11.940
It looks like the places are holding 
steady as the race continues.

00:19:11.940 --> 00:19:14.690
Coming into the third corner, 
there'll be an ascent.

00:19:14.690 --> 00:19:17.690
Nanto Mist is still leading the way.

00:19:16.380 --> 00:19:20.380
I'd hold back here and make 
my move on the next corner.

00:19:20.970 --> 00:19:24.490
It looks like Nice Nature and Rionatal, 
along with Breath Ooon Dance,

00:19:24.490 --> 00:19:26.450
#8 in the red, are making their move!

00:19:26.740 --> 00:19:29.780
All 18 racers have bunched up again, and 
this race is turning out quite remarkably!

00:19:29.780 --> 00:19:31.210
Just look at them go!

00:19:31.210 --> 00:19:32.780
It's anyone's game!

00:19:33.310 --> 00:19:35.920
And this is where I would pick it up!

00:19:37.070 --> 00:19:38.640
And get out in front!

00:19:43.020 --> 00:19:46.370
And no one can catch up to me.

00:19:51.640 --> 00:19:52.730
Prez...

00:20:14.310 --> 00:20:15.560
Rionatal is now in the lead!

00:20:15.560 --> 00:20:17.630
But Nice Nature is closing in!

00:20:17.960 --> 00:20:20.710
I won't let them say it, 
I won't, I swear I won't!

00:20:20.710 --> 00:20:23.240
I won't let anyone wonder about how this 
would've turned out if Teio was running!

00:20:25.180 --> 00:20:27.570
I'm not gonna lose to Teio!

00:20:27.570 --> 00:20:29.560
We're better than her!

00:20:29.790 --> 00:20:31.430
We're better!

00:20:31.430 --> 00:20:33.450
I swear we're better!

00:20:40.310 --> 00:20:41.260
Go...

00:20:42.910 --> 00:20:47.140
Go! Run!

00:20:47.140 --> 00:20:48.830
Rionatal! Rionatal!

00:20:48.830 --> 00:20:50.870
She crosses the goal in first place!

00:20:51.410 --> 00:20:54.830
The Kikkashou was a tight contest, 
but she came out on top!

00:20:56.750 --> 00:20:58.130
I did it!

00:21:02.180 --> 00:21:03.880
Damn it!

00:21:03.880 --> 00:21:05.590
Fourth place! Good effort!

00:21:12.980 --> 00:21:16.020
It's no fair, how they all looked so cool.

00:21:16.480 --> 00:21:17.380
Teio...

00:21:17.850 --> 00:21:20.570
Sorry about the holdup. Here you go.

00:21:21.420 --> 00:21:22.380
Thanks!

00:21:24.350 --> 00:21:25.400
Let's head home.

00:21:27.620 --> 00:21:30.470
Hey, Trainer... they were all amazing, huh?

00:21:30.470 --> 00:21:32.040
Well, yeah.

00:21:32.430 --> 00:21:35.490
They all went into the 
Kikkashou with a lot of drive.

00:21:35.490 --> 00:21:37.940
The ones who raced you in the Derby...

00:21:37.940 --> 00:21:40.250
The ones who fought tooth 
and nail to enter...

00:21:40.670 --> 00:21:41.940
The same goes for you, right?

00:21:41.940 --> 00:21:42.840
Me?

00:21:42.840 --> 00:21:46.270
Wasn't all of that hard rehab so 
that you could win the Kikkashou

00:21:46.270 --> 00:21:49.510
and become an undefeated Triple Crown winner?

00:21:49.510 --> 00:21:51.370
I didn't make it in time, though..

00:21:52.070 --> 00:21:55.400
Aw, come on, don't look so sad!

00:21:59.060 --> 00:22:01.560
I've realized something, you know.

00:22:02.350 --> 00:22:07.420
I couldn't win the Triple Crown...
 but I haven't lost.

00:22:08.350 --> 00:22:09.410
Teio?

00:22:10.000 --> 00:22:13.360
So I can still be undefeated, can't I?

00:22:19.170 --> 00:22:22.380
Yeah, you're right! You can 
be an undefeated horse girl!

00:22:23.080 --> 00:22:24.800
Which means I'm gonna need 
to come up with a plan

00:22:24.800 --> 00:22:26.610
for your training once 
you're back in action.

00:22:26.610 --> 00:22:27.710
Sounds like fun!

00:22:27.710 --> 00:22:29.220
I'm counting on you, trainer!

00:22:29.220 --> 00:22:31.220
Yeah, leave it to me!

00:22:31.830 --> 00:22:34.190
Please lower your voices while on the train.

00:22:34.190 --> 00:22:35.330
Sorry.

